    {
      "type": "sign",
      "pos": [
        -0.5,
        0.0,
        2.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 3.141592653589793,
      "message": "THE MURK SENATE\n\nA roundtable of seven walkers in the fog. They are arguing about settings nobody set, on a thing nobody can name, with consequences nobody can describe.\n\nThey have been at it for some time."
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        -0.5,
        0.0,
        -1.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 0.0,
      "name": "Senator Olm",
      "body_color": [
        0.55,
        0.55,
        0.6,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.4,
        0.42,
        0.45,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Listen",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Senator Olm",
            "text": "The number wants to be lower. I have always said the number wants to be lower."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        1.5,
        0.0,
        -0.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": -0.6,
      "name": "Senator Bethel",
      "body_color": [
        0.5,
        0.55,
        0.6,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.45,
        0.42,
        0.4,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Listen",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Senator Bethel",
            "text": "The number cannot be lower. Olm has been wrong about the number for a long time."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        1.5,
        0.0,
        0.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": -1.2,
      "name": "Senator Reska",
      "body_color": [
        0.6,
        0.55,
        0.55,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.42,
        0.4,
        0.42,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Listen",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Senator Reska",
            "text": "The number must be considered carefully. We have been considering it carefully for some time."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        0.5,
        0.0,
        1.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": -2.0,
      "name": "Senator Pell",
      "body_color": [
        0.55,
        0.6,
        0.6,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.4,
        0.42,
        0.42,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Listen",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Senator Pell",
            "text": "Friends, friends \u2014 perhaps the number is not the right question. Perhaps the right question is which of us last knew the question."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        -0.5,
        0.0,
        1.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 2.0,
      "name": "Senator Ulor",
      "body_color": [
        0.5,
        0.55,
        0.55,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.4,
        0.4,
        0.42,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Listen",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Senator Ulor",
            "text": "Pell is changing the subject again. Pell is always changing the subject. Khorgaul's grip, Pell."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        -1.5,
        0.0,
        0.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 1.2,
      "name": "Senator Velna",
      "body_color": [
        0.55,
        0.55,
        0.6,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.45,
        0.42,
        0.4,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Listen",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Senator Velna",
            "text": "Move that we adjourn. ...Move that we have always adjourned. ...Move that we begin to consider a motion to perhaps adjourn."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "npc",
      "pos": [
        -1.5,
        0.0,
        -0.5
      ],
      "rotation_y": 0.6,
      "name": "Senator Marn",
      "body_color": [
        0.6,
        0.55,
        0.55,
        1.0
      ],
      "hat_color": [
        0.42,
        0.4,
        0.42,
        1.0
      ],
      "idle_hint": "[E] Listen",
      "dialog_tree": {
        "start": "root",
        "nodes": {
          "root": {
            "speaker": "Senator Marn",
            "text": "Walker \u2014 would you cast the deciding voice? ...No, I see, the question has shifted again. Never mind. Walk well."
          }
        }
      }
    }
